ji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d313103ab346bec048c6f9712aa52e86c445b319","tid":1155593,"uid":49216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T05:36:05.000Z","msg":"快啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n得把口，要錢未開個價囉<br />\n吹到咁大，做唔到好樣衰架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b17a71f7bd3e7b035084c6d8364973fa3612f1c","tid":1155593,"uid":162095,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T05:36:14.000Z","msg":"想睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fe5405b00aaed9e07a62aecf0285fbbb203e89f","tid":1155593,"uid":35098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T05:36:17.000Z","msg":"唔做正仆街！ 快啲去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25a0348c49cc48db260ea8e86573d8d4bed19b50","tid":1155593,"uid":53254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T05:37:20.000Z","msg":"開心過aia嘉年華"},{"pid":"a275ace3c0270575234143f536e684798d11e0f9","tid":1155593,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T05:38:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd98ed1a0c7c4c353d4acbe0215328eaba1698c9","tid":1155593,"uid":182499,"like"